  "fn": "convertZhihuArticleHtml",
  "args": [
    "<div class=\"Post-RichTextContainer\"><div class=\"css-1od93p9\"><div class=\"css-376mun\"><div class=\"css-h7wqi8\"><div class=\"css-168dvon\"><div class=\"css-lcgmxk\"><div><div class=\"Catalog isCatalogV2 css-2hy5iv\" data-za-detail-view-name=\"正文\"><div class=\"css-8kjoqe\"><div class=\"css-u56wtg\"><span style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center;\">​<svg width=\"1.2em\" height=\"1.2em\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--Catalog24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M10 5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h10a1 1 0 1 1 0 2H11a1 1 0 0 1-1-1Zm4 6a1 1 0 1 0 0 2h7a1 1 0 1 0 0-2h-7Zm0 7a1 1 0 1 0 0 2h7a1 1 0 1 0 0-2h-7Zm-8.335.25a.915.915 0 0 1-.915-.915V12.75H10a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5H4.75V6.665c0-.505.41-.915.915-.915H7a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5H5.665A2.415 2.415 0 0 0 3.25 6.665v10.67a2.415 2.415 0 0 0 2.415 2.415H10a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5H5.665Z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"css-1czzy4f\">目录</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span id=\"content\"><div class=\"RichText ztext Post-RichText css-yzps3a\" options=\"[object Object]\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"OidvS5rH\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2013669483248633430\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\" data-za-detail-view-id=\"1043\">上一篇</a><sup data-text=\"\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2013669483248633430\" data-numero=\"1\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-tooltip=\"&lt;a href=&quot;https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2013669483248633430&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2013669483248633430&lt;/a&gt;\" data-tooltip-richtext=\"1\" data-tooltip-preset=\"white\" data-tooltip-classname=\"ztext-reference-tooltip\"><a id=\"ref_1_0\" href=\"#ref_1\" data-reference-link=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"ref_1\">[1]</a></sup>介绍了Qwen3.5和MiniMax2.5的结构。本篇主要聚焦于采用<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=271407567&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=DSA&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">DSA<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>（DeepSeek Sparse Attention）作为注意力机制的两款模型：GLM 5和<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=271407567&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=DeepSeek+V3.2&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">DeepSeek V3.2<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。GLM 5是智谱于2026年2月发布的大语言模型，采用自研的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=271407567&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=Slime%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">Slime框架<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>进行训练。DeepSeek V3.2的实验版本于2025年9月发布，正式版则于同年12月推出，其核心工作围绕提升训练与推理的性价比展开。值得注意的是，GLM 5的架构与DeepSeek V3.2基本相同，主要区别在于参数配置。本文将重点介绍这两款模型的架构。</p><h2 id=\"h_2015756101291894133_0\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">1 GLM 5</h2><p data-pid=\"-q65Ef15\">GLM 5模型是一款大语言模型（LLM）采用<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=271407567&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=MLA&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">MLA<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>(DSA) + <span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=271407567&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=MoE&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">MoE<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>结构，总参数量为774B，推理时激活的参数为40B。 从GLM 4.x到GLM 5结构上最大变化是Attention部分从<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=271407567&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=GQA&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">GQA<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>变为了DSA，与DeepSeekV3.2类似。</p><p data-pid=\"ZgxrdkG1\"><b>效果：</b>在SWE-bench-Verified和Terminal Bench 2.0中分别获得77.8和56.2的开源模型分数，性能表现超过<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=271407567&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=Gemini+3.0+Pro&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini 3.0 Pro<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。</p><p data-pid=\"jMv6c36V\"><b>性能：</b>由于采用了DSA，在保持长上下文能力的同时降低了部署成本。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><div class=\"RichText-ConditionalImagePortal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bdb48aa685185e4e8c5a0586b34d30a1_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1222\" data-rawheight=\"1168\" data-original-token=\"v2-0950bb46fd92e5228aa1ae5725b2fd82\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1222\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bdb48aa685185e4e8c5a0586b34d30a1_r.jpg\"></div></figure><blockquote data-pid=\"o4kGr54N\">高清图地址：<span class=\"nolink\">https://github.com/CalvinXKY/InfraTech/tree/main/models/glm_5</span></blockquote><h3 id=\"h_2015756101291894133_1\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\"><b>1.1 整体特点</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"zfNJRvVL\">模型前三层使用Dense结构，后面层使用MoE结构。</li><li data-pid=\"lrskWYHc\">Attention模块：  </li><ul><li data-pid=\"5g60BGwE\">主体使用MLA结构</li><li data-pid=\"mZ35H-d5\">采用DSA进行稀疏处理</li></ul><li data-pid=\"1SPa3dNT\">稀疏相关模块：</li><ul><li data-pid=\"UkmXt1y6\">Lightning Indexer: 计算出每个Q值与历史的所有K/V值的关联关系(相关性)，得到一个分数排序；</li><li data-pid=\"DYytEOTN\">Top-k Selector: 选出分数最高的k个K/V进行注意力计算，实现稀疏Attention。</li></ul><li data-pid=\"nbJW1iC0\">支持序列长度200k</li></ul><h3 id=\"h_2015756101291894133_2\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\"><b>1.2 模型结构描述</b></h3><p data-pid=\"wPapjj7o\">MLA参数配置：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">q_lora_rank=2048\nqk_rope_head_dim=64\nkv_lora_rank=512\nqk_nope_head_dim=192\nqk_rope_head_dim=64\nqk_head_dim(nope+rope)=256\nheads(num_attention_heads)=64\nv_head_dim=256</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"oHlJY3qK\">Indexer参数配置：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">index_topk=2048\nindex_head_dim=128\nindex_n_heads=32\nqk_rope_head_dim=64\nqk_nope_head_dim=192</code></pre></div><figure data-size=\"normal\"><div class=\"RichText-ConditionalImagePortal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ff221d4cd5a6ace509667497533ada74_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"866\" data-rawheight=\"1001\" data-original-token=\"v2-2268f7357fdf923c45619200f2f08f87\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"866\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ff221d4cd5a6ace509667497533ada74_r.jpg\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"VTmtXYs2\"><b>MoE模块</b></p><p data-pid=\"MtH8WQEY\">独立专家+共享专家，单token仅8个独立专家计算。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><div class=\"RichText-ConditionalImagePortal\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-40b1cb4da723faeb763624f516d385ed_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1053\" data-rawheight=\"355\" data-original-token=\"v2-ddf1b41bbb1eb1f46bb492b02eba4a8a\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1053\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-40b1cb4da723faeb763624f516d385ed_r.jpg\"></div></figure><h3 id=\"h_2015756101291894133_3\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\"><b>1.3 相关资料</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"8LBfdwTk\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/text/glm-5\" class=\"wrap external ctz-link-changed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">整体介绍（官方博客）</a></li><li data-pid=\"r86UPsC2\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-5/blob/main/config.json\" class=\"wrap external ctz-link-changed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">模型配置文件</a></li><li data-pid=\"TyH38gwm\"><a href=\"https://github.com/huggingface/transformers/tree/main/src/transformers/models/glm_moe_dsa\" class=\"wrap external ctz-link-changed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Transformer模型定义</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"h_2015756101291894133_4\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\"><b>2 DeepSeek V3.2</b></h2><p data-pid=\"9h2k_Efd\">DeepSeek V3.2是一款大语言模型，其核心特点在于引入了DeepSeek Sparse Attention（DSA）机制，在V3.1-Terminus的基础上显著降低了计算复杂度。该系列首先推出了实验版本V3.2-Exp，随后发布了正式版本V3.2和V3.2-Speciale。模型总参数量为671B，推理时仅激活37B参数。</p><p data-pid=\"UIKPnOrv\"><b>效果：</b>DeepSeek-V3.2-Speciale超越了GPT-5，并表现出与Gemini-3.0-Pro相当的推理能力。<br><br><b>性能：</b>在保持几乎相同的模型输出质量的同时，大幅提高了长上下文训练和推理效率。</p><h3 id=\"h_2015756101291894133_5\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\"><b>2.1 整体特点</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"YPFn2Mj3\">Attention 模块： </li><ul><li data-pid=\"GLjkynZC\">DSA：在MLA的基础上增加了Indexer模块，用于控制KV值中参与计算的tokens数量。</li><li data-pid=\"16TIp_81\">Decode阶段，tokens数量限定在2k以内，因此MLA的计算量与context长度无关。</li><li data-pid=\"6gFdzEH4\">支持上下文长度：128K。</li></ul></ul><figure data-size=\"normal\"><div class=\"RichText-ConditionalImagePortal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1d91653517c749ed8f6fcc1ade6d98f9_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1196\" data-rawheight=\"1139\" data-original-token=\"v2-ef8911689f24a380f46d0a742dc16fb0\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1196\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1d91653517c749ed8f6fcc1ade6d98f9_r.jpg\"></div></figure><blockquote data-pid=\"uahGTDvx\">高清图地址：<span class=\"nolink\">https://github.com/CalvinXKY/InfraTech/tree/main/models/deepseek_v3_2</span></blockquote><h3 id=\"h_2015756101291894133_6\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\"><b>2.2 模型结构描述</b></h3><p data-pid=\"ObsSUYS0\">MLA参数配置：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">q_lora_rank=2048\nqk_rope_head_dim=64\nkv_lora_rank=512\nqk_nope_head_dim=192\nqk_rope_head_dim=64\nqk_head_dim(nope+rope)=256\nheads(num_attention_heads)=64\nv_head_dim=256</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"bk2xOTni\">Indexer参数配置：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">index_topk=2048\nindex_head_dim=128\nindex_n_heads=32\nqk_rope_head_dim=64\nqk_nope_head_dim=192</code></pre></div><figure data-size=\"normal\"><div class=\"RichText-ConditionalImagePortal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-52a16ab239d3f3e18b7b4d5d30d1940d_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"849\" data-rawheight=\"973\" data-original-token=\"v2-8ca7d62ff41ad1207158c7929259ca2b\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"849\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-52a16ab239d3f3e18b7b4d5d30d1940d_r.jpg\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"hwlpa-O4\"><b>MoE模块</b></p><p data-pid=\"K0LuX7d4\">独立专家+共享专家，单token仅8个独立专家计算。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><div class=\"RichText-ConditionalImagePortal\"><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c184b34fd6e0ca0c4ec520b26a88699f_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1036\" data-rawheight=\"357\" data-original-token=\"v2-efd288175b0243b41de1a32c8aa3f1e8\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1036\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c184b34fd6e0ca0c4ec520b26a88699f_r.jpg\"></div></figure><h3 id=\"h_2015756101291894133_7\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\"><b>2.3 相关资料</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"HaJgbeH-\"><a href=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp/blob/main/DeepSeek_V3_2.pdf\" class=\"wrap external ctz-link-changed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">整体介绍（官方博客）</a></li><li data-pid=\"GdoZl1bm\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.2/blob/main/config.json\" class=\"wrap external ctz-link-changed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">模型配置文件</a></li><li data-pid=\"6b-XtETv\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.2/tree/main/inference\" class=\"wrap external ctz-link-changed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">模型定义示例</a></li></ul><p data-pid=\"difuhlSO\">模型相关的内容跳转至：<a href=\"https://github.com/CalvinXKY/InfraTech/tree/main/models/\" class=\"external ctz-link-changed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/CalvinXKY/In</span><span class=\"invisible\">fraTech/tree/main/models/</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"TfFLxZGr\">上一篇：</p><div class=\"RichText-LinkCardContainer\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2013669483248633430\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-text=\"2026大模型架构概览（一）：Qwen3.5&amp;MiniMax M2.5\" class=\"LinkCard new css-f4yf4o ctz-link-changed\"><span class=\"LinkCard-image LinkCard-image--default\"></span><span class=\"LinkCard-contents\"><span class=\"LinkCard-title loading\" data-text=\"true\"></span><span class=\"LinkCard-desc loading\"></span></span></a></div><hr><blockquote data-pid=\"wm-1u7SJ\">想深耕AI Infra领域？欢迎访问<a href=\"https://github.com/CalvinXKY/InfraTech\" class=\"wrap external ctz-link-changed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">InfraTech</a>库！内容涵盖大模型基础、PyTorch/vLLM/SGLang框架入门、性能